role_description: An Ansible role that installs s5cmd on nearly any platform
role_description_full_overview: This repository contains an Ansible role that installs s5cmd on nearly any platform. s5cmd is a very fast S3 and local filesystem execution tool. It comes with support for a multitude of operations including tab completion and wildcard support for files, which can be very handy for your object storage workflow while working with large number of files.
